          "German verb prefixes have SYSTEMATIC meanings:",
          "",
          "herunter- = down (separable)",
          "herunterladen (download - load down)",
          "herunterfallen (fall down)",
          "",
          "über- = over, across, too much (inseparable)",
          "überweisen (transfer), übertreiben (exaggerate)",
          "überraschen (surprise), übernehmen (take over)",
          "",
          "ver- = away, wrongly, completion (inseparable)",
          "verkaufen (sell), vergessen (forget)",
          "verstehen (understand), verlieren (lose)",
          "",
          "ent- = away from, removal (inseparable)",
          "entdecken (discover), entscheiden (decide)",
          "enttäuschen (disappoint), entwickeln (develop)",
          "",
          "Understanding prefixes helps decode new words!"
